Classes

class  TestFileGenerator

Detailed Description

This defines a class that generates test data files. This is not really a test fixture. Once the files are generated they still have to be copied to data/data or parsers/data or fusion/data folders. To generate a file, the method that generates it must be uncommented in GenerateTestFiles.
